    <div class="summary">
        <h3><a href="/questions/8819/portfolio-optimization-with-absolute-position-constraints" class="question-hyperlink">Portfolio optimization with absolute position constraints</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
            I'm looking to optimize a portfolio maximizing expected return for a particular risk budget, but with absolute constraints on the individual instrument positions. 

I've been experimenting with QP, ...
